Sentencas: Nickel zirconia, Ni-YSZ, porous cermets used in solid oxide fuel cells can be considered as composite materials consisting of three phases, namely nickel (Ni), ytrria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ), and voids.
Titulo: Effective modulus and coefficient of thermal expansion of Ni-YSZ porous cermets

Sentencas: Based on Ni-YSZ's microstructural features, such as the volume fractions, average particle sizes and their correlations of a physical sample, a three-dimensional stochastic reconstruction method is used to recreate the three-phase composite.
Titulo: Effective modulus and coefficient of thermal expansion of Ni-YSZ porous cermets

Sentencas: The digitally reconstructed microstructure is then transferred into finite element models to obtain the material's corresponding effective elastic modulus and effective coefficient of thermal expansion at various temperatures.
Titulo: Effective modulus and coefficient of thermal expansion of Ni-YSZ porous cermets

Sentencas: Predictions from such a numerical methodology agree well with experimental results.
Titulo: Effective modulus and coefficient of thermal expansion of Ni-YSZ porous cermets
